# Math or Merit?

Everyone starts equal. Every trade is fair. One person ends up with almost
everything.

This is the Yard-Sale model: two people meet, risk the same fraction of the
poorer person's wealth, and give either person an equal chance to win.

Agents: {engine.config.n}  
